{"tid":1316142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意逆轉？  轉黎我地果面就真！","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:39:40.000Z","uid":27111,"like":226,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5c2f32038b1f77c8d812f5795b6c4a3d3be7bb","tid":1316142,"uid":27111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"老母不嬲都終極左膠中立撚。 次次都話遊行冇所謂，總之衝就唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱我同佢解釋班狗又叫人走又圍住班手足黎拉，佢已經冇出聲。心諗今次竟然唔屌我地衝？<br />\n<br />\n點知，去到新城市，影到有幾個手足俾人拉左。我竟然見到我老母眼濕濕！！ 佢話後生細仔又唔係打家劫舍咁樣就冇左前途好慘，仲屌啲政府高層玩失蹤，製造民怨。<br />\n<br />\n果下我真係當堂喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿媽你終於醒<br />\n我老母仲話要去17號同21號和理非遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好放棄</span>，我地係有希望嫁！！！"},{"pid":"de51a7f0f45a6ac55ac33b5903cc8a9fcb69e765","tid":1316142,"uid":108337,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"不切割 冷處理 無條件支持同路人"},{"pid":"0cd0a544407e194564ddf4629ac617a1dff38939","tid":1316142,"uid":57081,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"我老母都係 但唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d57c6604a943577f29c82410014d5720a526938","tid":1316142,"uid":47208,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"0cd0a544407e194564ddf4629ac617a1dff38939","tid":1316142,"uid":57081,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"我老母都係 但唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"+ 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係人皆有惻忍之心<br />\n特別係有仔女既父母"},{"pid":"9813be5d489134f40887653d07c648d1f2c18cec","tid":1316142,"uid":55493,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"廣傳畀人知 遊行未完 不反對通知書未夠鐘<br />\n已經畀人包圍咗，然後逼市民入商場避難，再瓮中捉鱉，針對特定政治取態嘅市民"},{"pid":"b15eada073c32e59cc33b13974c3ac1cb595737d","tid":1316142,"uid":32861,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eON3JXp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeON3JXp.png&h=3e38b578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n急"},{"pid":"051eef4f42b831c3c660f2b3000c9b4d76ab5151","tid":1316142,"uid":86643,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"我阿媽都話今晚班人係香港英雄<br />\n頭先我真係開住RTHK32同佢地睇咗個幾兩個鐘Live<br />\n睇住警察點樣毆落市民到<br />\n睇住警察扯爛個細路件衫抆低佢條褲<br />\n<br />\n佢地最後都明白到<br />\n呢D畫面佢地唔會可以係TVB睇到"},{"pid":"6c9812440b55c0dbf7f7c1ea1d83e7ed9e50ce7a","tid":1316142,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"淨係睇到商場圍嘔市民"},{"pid":"a9040c69a5031a625c8a39d68f9a6358e4d6d7d0","tid":1316142,"uid":37596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"最重要黑警衝入商場, 同&quot;共產黨打到來&quot;無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb2e29b31054f51519aedd6c426026a04289225","tid":1316142,"uid":62270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"我個中立老母都話係班黑警包圍唔比人走離晒普"},{"pid":"ba373b5586f8ef35134c911912988a0f94d84d45","tid":1316142,"uid":57081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb2e29b31054f51519aedd6c426026a04289225","tid":1316142,"uid":62270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"我個中立老母都話係班黑警包圍唔比人走離晒普"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"我都係<img s