日接觸唔同嘅資訊，無綫播咩佢地睇咩，先會覺得我地好暴力。"},{"pid":"a58f9b96316c6dcd2c44551b0038005db903e5c8","tid":1316142,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"我老豆港豬 都話：「哦！原來如此」就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fbc7c93fbb90a2ddd17fa57c40b42d3dbf6925","tid":1316142,"uid":46688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ee93ccd17da4df35a771d78ff0e1d20a903459","tid":1316142,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"我老母都係"},{"pid":"ec681ab6858641d6dd97588545ecc05fc050bc16","tid":1316142,"uid":104165,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb849f3374cfec5447f853944923ace4e6def07","tid":1316142,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"要大大宣傳衝入新城市既片<br />\n俾長輩睇<br />\n<br />\n擺明人地係商場<br />\n咁樣衝上去"},{"pid":"fc3817122bb668dadec36863c8f4a99301afbaf6","tid":1316142,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"主要原因係呢個政府同呢隊警隊太過乞人憎"},{"pid":"18cf5d6e67016ddd83a705a921189f06ce574128","tid":1316142,"uid":126099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"我老母一講黑警就好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0526b82981b1bc502f3b84cd44b769a97edeefd4","tid":1316142,"uid":32502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"各個group 見到d打柒黑警既片都表示治愈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9556eecaf12377de383cb0fcbc094e82f5b0f31","tid":1316142,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockqu